assets.name: assets/3Z_-xRX-AaV
assets.description:
1st model,  getting to know Tiltbrush with a parallax style magnifying glass scene.

Made a textured wall with the paper brush that will act as a magnified wall, with a marker brush on top to hide the topology of an unmagnified wall.
Threw in a little hole for the magnifying glass to look through and scaled the splat in the back wall.
